    <a title="Dawn Michelle" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/316327-dawn-michelle"><img alt="Dawn Michelle" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1533581221p2/316327.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3185218379?book_show_action=true">Feb 19, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dawn Michelle" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dawn Michelle" href="/user/show/316327-dawn-michelle">Dawn Michelle</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/26849837-death-of-a-cozy-writer">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/316327-dawn-michelle?shelf=audiobook-hoopla">audiobook-hoopla</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/316327-dawn-michelle?shelf=kindle-carnegie-library">kindle-carnegie-library</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/316327-dawn-michelle?shelf=books-read-in-2020">books-read-in-2020</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/316327-dawn-michelle?shelf=cozy-mystery-read">cozy-mystery-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/316327-dawn-michelle?shelf=kindle-read">kindle-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/316327-dawn-michelle?shelf=2020-facebook-cozy-challenge">2020-facebook-cozy-challenge</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3185218379" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16100958300837711028">Do yourself a favor and skip this series and just stick with her Max Tudor series [WHICH is delightful]. This was not delightful, had a not-so-great narrator and the story generally was meh [and while I am not a prude, this had more language than I was expecting and seemed gratuitous for a cozy mystery]. The end was good and somewhat unexpected so that helped keep it at 2 stars, but I generally feel like I totally wasted my time. :-(</span>

          </span>
        </div>


