        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer202728415" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1895902279159753243">This was a typical murder mystery: the suspects sequestered in the mansion; the detective gathering them to identify the killer. It was an entertaining, fast-paced read. The only item keeping me from giving it five stars is how the mystery was solved. The detective used information that we readers did not have - making it impossible for me to make a decent guess. This won&apos;t keep me from reading another one, though. It was a fun, easy read!</span>
  <span id="freeText1895902279159753243" style="display:none">This was a typical murder mystery: the suspects sequestered in the mansion; the detective gathering them to identify the killer. It was an entertaining, fast-paced read. The only item keeping me from giving it five stars is how the mystery was solved. The detective used information that we readers did not have - making it impossible for me to make a decent guess. This won't keep me from reading another one, though. It was a fun, easy read!</span>
